---
import Base from '../../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="登记成功 · SIPA 校友圈">

<div style="min-height:80vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; background:#f8f7f4; padding:3rem 1.5rem; text-align:center;">
  <div style="max-width:460px;">
    <div style="font-size:3rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">🎉</div>
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-stone-900 mb-3">已收到，谢谢！</h1>
    <p style="color:#888; font-size:0.9375rem; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
      你的信息我已收到。校友圈还在建设中，我会在合适的时候联系你。<br/>
      如果有任何问题，也可以直接发邮件到
      <a href="mailto:yh3811@columbia.edu" class="text-columbia-navy no-underline hover:underline">yh3811@columbia.edu</a>。
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.75rem; justify-content:center;">
      <a href="/alumni/"
         class="no-underline px-6 py-2.5 bg-columbia-navy text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        返回校友圈
      </a>
      <a href="/"
         class="no-underline px-6 py-2.5 bg-white border border-stone-200 text-stone-700 text-sm rounded-full hover:bg-stone-50 transition-colors">
        回首页看看
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</Base>
